{"word":"G4952 - συσπαράσσω - sysparássō - soos-par-as'-so - Throw down","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συσπαράσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sysparássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soos-par-as'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Throw down</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அலைக்கழி"},{"paragraph":"to convulse completely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4682 - σπαράσσω - sparássō - spar-as'-so/4682\">G4682</a>; to <i>rend completely</i>, that is, (by analogy) to <i>convulse</i> violently: - throw down.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}